I"üL<p>It took me time to see Mary Cassatt. And then she saw me. The following is a bit of a love-letter:</p>

<div class="ImageComponent ImageComponent--medium" id="feed-me__cassatt-childs-bath"><figure>
    <div class="ImageComponent--image-wrapper flex align-center">
